            "title": "緬甸地震︱陳國基赴京迎接中國救援隊回國 晚上機場辦特區救援隊迎接儀式",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"緬甸地震︱陳國基赴京迎接中國救援隊回國 晚上機場辦特區救援隊迎接儀式\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/81fa1460bb53cdfe4b85feb262b4ccc4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250408/_2025040823462418109.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">緬甸地震︱陳國基赴京迎接中國救援隊回國 晚上機場辦特區救援隊迎接儀式</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>特區政府公布，政務司司長陳國基將於明日（9日）早上前赴北京，出席迎接中國救援隊隊員（包括香港隊員）由緬甸回國的儀式；保安局局長鄧炳強和消防處處長楊恩健同人。3人同日將聯同香港特區救援隊隊員返港，預計晚上抵港。特區政府將於香港國際機場為香港隊員舉行迎接儀式。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184623/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳國基將到北京迎接中國救援隊回國。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61756f690e8d347d980b00c243836c98/2025-04/NA250226PA052.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳國基將到北京迎接中國救援隊回國。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184620/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強（左二）和楊恩健（左三）會隨行。圖為特區救援隊前往緬甸時機場送行。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3db837ad848cc636685e4e440c25350b/2025-04/NK250329EH37.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強（左二）和楊恩健（左三）會隨行。圖為特區救援隊前往緬甸時機場送行。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184621/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97c93c2a3708cfd7d0067cfd71ae909d/2025-04/NK250329EH35.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184622/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef37827497e946ceb2aea097c01de49b/2025-04/NK250329EH36.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184624/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"香港寄送救援物資到緬甸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c4d95908d2528dc64257d059fb10562/2025-04/C6AAEE3BB4C74BA49936F61DD347222D_O.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港寄送救援物資到緬甸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184625/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"香港寄送救援物資到緬甸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10c3d254c42b3fb0447f893cd249c570/2025-04/8D9DE6E43ACD41838C95832A23BF221A_O_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港寄送救援物資到緬甸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
