        {
            "title": "Coldplay演唱會︱為避散場人潮 樂迷不等完騷 周一鳴到場視察",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Coldplay演唱會︱為避散場人潮 樂迷不等完騷 周一鳴到場視察\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/42bff2dc6569ba578015f5a493be4ab3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250408/_2025040823225526595.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Coldplay演唱會︱為避散場人潮 樂迷不等完騷 周一鳴到場視察</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【Coldplay香港演唱會/英國樂隊/啟德體育園/離場/散場】英國樂隊Coldplay今晚（8日）在啟德體育園主場館開唱，《星島頭條》在場內外直擊，有部分觀眾晚上約10時05分提早離開，到晚上10時15分，繼續有大批歌迷湧出，但場內演唱會仍未結束。有來自中山的樂迷指，為了避開散場人潮、趕直通巴士回內地。有觀眾盛讚現場氣氛「非常正」，雖然演唱會延遲近30分鐘開始，但表演一流，又感受到歌手們對香港的熱情，希望他們以後有機會到內地城市巡演。至晚上10時35分，4名樂隊成員在台上與觀眾揮手道別，隨後轉身離開舞台，演唱會結束。\n\n</p>\n<p>曾任啟德體育園的跨部門演練小組執行長的警務處處長周一鳴亦「重臨舊地」，今晚到場視察。他接受《星島頭條》訪問時表示，會持續觀察和留意散場情況。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"Coldplay%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E7%B6%AB%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%87%B3%E7%B4%8425%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E4%B8%80%E7%8F%AD-%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%B7%9A%E5%BE%80%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9D%87%E6%B8%85%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%20%7C%20%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%20https%3A//www.stheadline.com/society/3445179/\">Coldplay演唱會︱港鐵屯馬綫加密至約2.5分鐘一班 特別巴士線往口岸 一文睇清離場安排</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184590/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警務處處長周一鳴到場視察。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02288c2030120a0b9e360eb9aabae3b6/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_232155827_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警務處處長周一鳴到場視察。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184591/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"周一鳴指會持續觀察和留意散場情況。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/872fa9619280877800cf9abde8d8c888/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_232155827_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周一鳴指會持續觀察和留意散場情況。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184592/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"周一嗚視察散場情況。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db075e54d9e448fac461f54ab6fc152d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_232155827_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周一嗚視察散場情況。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184593/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"周一鳴曾任啟德體育園的跨部門演練小組執行長。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6b13c1d92bde756c26e9c2f01458321/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_232155827_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周一鳴曾任啟德體育園的跨部門演練小組執行長。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184589/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"周一鳴。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/abc0c11da07d659f6020f3ac5c44f2ec/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_232155827.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周一鳴。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2><strong>姚柏良田北辰讚音響氣氛一流</strong></h2>\n<p>晚上10點前已經離場的旅遊界立法會議員姚柏良接受《星島頭條》訪問時表示，對演唱會非常滿意，場館音效和氣氛均「超一流」。他指，部分入場旅客會留港過夜，相信今晚過境服務能夠應付，又稱已了解到部分酒店訂單量令人滿意，直言「香港需要文藝流行盛事」。\n\n</p>\n<p>實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰亦和家人一起入場觀看，指今晚是第一次「真真正正感受到呢個主場館場嘅威力」，無論音響和現場氣氛都非常震撼，全場座無虛席，希望香港未來能舉辦更多類似盛事。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184554/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"旅遊界立法會議員姚柏良提早於10時前已離場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/547f61ceab7e1d5156b805fc52fc39aa/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-08_at_11_05_39_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        旅遊界立法會議員姚柏良提早於10時前已離場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184566/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"田北辰指現場非常震撼。田北辰fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/63eb3781583163aab653a534ccb04741/2025-04/489326867_1175832930573704_2974186890398810456_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        田北辰指現場非常震撼。田北辰fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184558/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批樂迷離場。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f39efe80be320e6c922cb56d1142a79/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_225909597_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批樂迷離場。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184559/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f75f0215ea9be08f6603fedc245ad09e/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250408_231309441_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\